The Fall - Series 2, Episode 4




Episode Four

Gibson reports to Burns that their confrontation in her hotel room may have been witnessed by Paul Spector. Gibson is further shocked to discover that Spector has been paying visits to one of his surviving victims in hospital. Seizing on the opportunity, Gibson finally locates Spector and puts him under surveillance.




Original Air Date: 30-Nov-2014
